name: Cheesy Muffins Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 cup skim milk (standard milk can be used)
120g tasty cheddar cheese, cut into 12 cubes

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 200Â°C. Grease a 12 hole medium muffin tin.
Sift flour into a large bowl and stir in grated cheese and vegetables.
Whisk milk, oil and egg together in a jug. Pour into flour mixture and mix together until just combined.
Spoon mixture evenly into the muffin tin. Push a cube of cheese into each; making sure it is covered with mixture. Bake for 25 minutes or until golden.
